msgid "Nesting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference/directives.md:170
msgid ""
"Begin/end regions can be nested. The inner `lang-check-end` closes the "
"most recent `lang-check-begin` (stack semantics):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference/directives.md:183
msgid "Interaction with Legacy Scope Markers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference/directives.md:185
msgid ""
"The `<!-- lang: xx -->` scope markers from `scoping.rs` continue to work."
" When both systems specify a language for the same position, the `lang-"
"check-begin lang:xx` directive takes precedence."
